data.stubGenerator:
read n:int
loop n read s:string(200)
write answer
data.inputDescription:
<<Line 1:>> An integer [[N]] for the number of strings to enter
<<Next [[N]] lines:>> String <<S>>

lastVersion.statementHTML:
Goal

Given a string S print first occurrence of all the characters present in that order only.
Input
Line 1: An integer N for the number of strings to enter
Next N lines: String S
Output
Desired Output
Constraints
S <= 200
Example
Input
2
aasdvasvavda
sajhags
Output
asdv
sajhg
